<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">Click, drag, or scroll with the touchpad</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents"><p class="p">If your system has a touchpad, you can click, double-click, drag, and scroll using only your
touchpad, without separate hardware buttons.</p></div>
<div id="clickordrag" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">Click or drag</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="p">You can click or drag using your touchpad.</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Click the <span class="em">system menu</span> <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/system-devices-panel.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="Power cog icon"></span></span> and
    select <span class="gui">System Settings</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Abra <span class="gui">Mur y touchpad</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Na seición <span class="gui">Touchpad</span>, marque <span class="gui">Activar pulsaciones del mur col touchpad</span>.</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<div class="list"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ul class="list" style="list-style-type:disc">
<li class="list"><p class="p">To click, tap once (but not in the bottom or top right-hand corners).</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">Pa facer una pulsación doble, toque dos vegaes.</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">To drag an item, tap twice but don't lift your finger after the second tap.
Drag the item where you want it, then lift your finger to drop.</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">To right-click, tap once in the bottom right-hand corner.</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">To middle-click, tap once in the top right-hand corner.</p></li>
</ul></div></div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div id="twofingerscroll" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">Desplazamientu con dos deos</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="p">Pue movese per duana del touchpad usando dos deos.</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Click the <span class="em">system menu</span> <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/system-devices-panel.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="Power cog icon"></span></span> and
    select <span class="gui">System Settings</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Abra <span class="gui">Mur y touchpad</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Na seición <span class="gui">Touchpad</span>, marque <span class="gui">Desplazamientu con dos deos</span>.</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<p class="p">When this is selected, tapping and dragging with one finger will work as normal, but if you drag two fingers across any part of the touchpad, it will scroll instead. If you also select <span class="gui">Enable horizontal scrolling</span>, you can move your fingers left and right to scroll horizontally. Be careful to space your fingers a bit apart. If your fingers are too close together, they just look like one big finger to your touchpad.</p>
<div class="note" title="Nota"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">El desplazamientu con dos deos pue nun funcionar en tolos touchpads.</p></div></div></div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div id="contentsticks" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">Adherencia del conteníu a los deos</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="p">Pue arrastrar el conteníu como si eslizare una pieza física de papel usando'l touchpad.</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Click the <span class="em">system menu</span> <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/system-devices-panel.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="Power cog icon"></span></span> and
    select <span class="gui">System Settings</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Abra <span class="gui">Mur y touchpad</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Na seición <span class="gui">Touchpad</span>, escueya <span class="gui">Adherencia del conteníu a los deos</span>.</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<div class="note" title="Nota"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">Esta carauterística tamién se conoz como <span class="em">Desplazamientu natural</span> o <span class="em">Desplazamientu inversu</span>.</p></div></div></div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
